                </Card>
                <Card author="Lujzi Jacsó">
                    She did a lovely job on my colour analysis! It really helped me to elevate my style and my wardrobe and really allowed me to experiment with different makeup styles. Couldn’t have asked for a more welcoming and professional experience☺️
